msgctxt "an5.205:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.205:0.2"
msgid "21. Kimilavagga "
msgstr "21. With Kimbila "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.205:0.3"
msgid "205. Cetokhilasutta "
msgstr "205. Emotional Barrenness "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.249, sc1
msgctxt "an5.205:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, cetokhilā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five kinds of emotional barrenness. "

msgctxt "an5.205:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.205:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satthari kaṅkhati vicikicchati nādhimuccati na sampasīdati. "
msgstr "Firstly, a mendicant has doubts about the Teacher. They’re uncertain, undecided, and lacking confidence. "

msgctxt "an5.205:1.4"
msgid "Yo so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satthari kaṅkhati vicikicchati nādhimuccati na sampasīdati, tassa cittaṃ na namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya. "
msgstr "This being so, their mind doesn’t incline toward keenness, commitment, persistence, and striving. "

msgctxt "an5.205:1.5"
msgid "Yassa cittaṃ na namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya, ayaṃ paṭhamo cetokhilo. "
msgstr "This is the first kind of emotional barrenness. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an5.205:2.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu dhamme kaṅkhati … pe … "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant has doubts about the teaching … "

msgctxt "an5.205:2.2"
msgid "saṅghe kaṅkhati … pe … "
msgstr "the Saṅgha … "

msgctxt "an5.205:2.3"
msgid "sikkhāya kaṅkhati … pe … "
msgstr "the training … "

msgctxt "an5.205:2.4"
msgid "sabrahmacārīsu kupito hoti anattamano āhatacitto khilajāto. "
msgstr "A mendicant is angry and upset with their spiritual companions, resentful and closed off. "

msgctxt "an5.205:2.5"
msgid "Yo so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sabrahmacārīsu kupito hoti anattamano āhatacitto khilajāto, tassa cittaṃ na namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya. "
msgstr "This being so, their mind doesn’t incline toward keenness, commitment, persistence, and striving. "

msgctxt "an5.205:2.6"
msgid "Yassa cittaṃ na namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya, ayaṃ pañcamo cetokhilo. "
msgstr "This is the fifth kind of emotional barrenness. "

msgctxt "an5.205:2.7"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca cetokhilā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the five kinds of emotional barrenness.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.205:2.8"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

